{"tid":1632290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又到凌晨時分，網軍又線啦","createTime":"2019-10-06T17:28:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T17:49:44.000Z","uid":242724,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e148c03f4f7986c62d140cae106a6fc2b10d6180","tid":1632290,"uid":242724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:28:59.000Z","msg":"仲上緊連登既你，小心分化POST，累既就訓啦，唔好上網住。"},{"pid":"712b7ff6b4432d95c3bc38a23cbc639ce75d7a5d","tid":1632290,"uid":294333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:29:23.000Z","msg":"（緊急）被黑的撞斷腳嘅女仔，眾籌去美國軍隊醫斷骨<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632054</a>"},{"pid":"4ad29c8cc1e31bda3b19b917ff5339adb24dcbf0","tid":1632290,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:29:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"9d22ab35edb2a7f2e76c1bb08ccb1509b6c0d7ce","tid":1632290,"uid":218298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:32:15.000Z","msg":"「認真」各位手足 借東風啊！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1629930\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1629930</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n麻煩幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"580e1bb9ad6fab40b49f233eb5f6f050430b0137","tid":1632290,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e148c03f4f7986c62d140cae106a6fc2b10d6180","tid":1632290,"uid":242724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:28:59.000Z","msg":"仲上緊連登既你，小心分化POST，累既就訓啦，唔好上網住。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:49:44.000Z","msg":"巴打你唔覺呢個鐘數，d post 先正常架咩？<br />\n<br />\n唉，睇一條片，教你點收啲黑紅藍皮，唔好話唔教精你地<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632259\" data-auto-link target=\"